      "originalText": "Supervisor + Skill Finder\n1. teacher confirms search terms\n2. `fetch_jobs` from Indeed + LinkedIn\n3. group job titles, teacher selects groups\n4. skill extractor subgraph: one LLM call per job\n5. merge / normalize `extracted_skills`\n6. teacher curates the approved skill set",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
